title: MisterMusic Show 328  indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 328 [120 minutes] 192 kbps MP3 stereo-


MisterMusic is back with new music from TV on the Radio, Cruisr, The Twilight Sad, and Courteeners. Plus a one-hit wonder from 1979 is the 'Oldie of the Week'. 
A song that topped the US chart in early November that year.

It's a two hour mish mash of indie, alternative and classic hits from over 5 decades of rock.



The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
